{"tid":1573254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[推比世界各地YouTuber]終於搵到個外國人幫手既方法啦","createTime":"2019-09-16T02:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T07:54:35.000Z","uid":184581,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b5167a1f52825ecc3d042f450f3a4f82425ff369","tid":1573254,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"離奇命案 都市傳說 呢幾樣野係世界各地都有一種吸引力<br />\n好似日本既離奇自殺/被殺 好多youtuber 都會講 仲要好多好多人睇<br />\n<br />\n香港最近發生左多單既懷疑[被自殺]案 警方都係話[冇可疑]<br />\n同時 呢場運動有好多外國人係好想幫我地 但唔知點幫<br />\n<br />\n係呢到 我諗左一個方向 可以做到3個效果<br />\n1.比外國人有個真正幫到香港既行動<br />\n2.做到一個國際既壓力 可以逼到831 CCTV<br />\n3.比國外人知香港警察有幾黑暗<br />\n<br />\n就係整合所有自殺案 翻譯成多國語言<br />\n希望各國網民幫手搵出真相<br />\n對外原因<br />\n1.原因係因為全世界都知既831事件 警方封左2日站 拒絕交出CCTV 很多人認為打死左人<br />\n2.831後出現多單離奇自殺案 認為是警方831打死人後 做出黎既[被自殺]案<br />\n3.希望各國網民可以幫忙找出真相<br />\n全香港<br />\n<br />\n有個巴打講得好好<br />\n過往好多時有人跳樓，家屬親友都會有路祭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548398/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548398/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1.北角浮屍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1549796/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1549796/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2.外籍女子跳樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569857/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569857/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3.朱植雄[被自殺]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569868/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569868/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569340/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569340/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比外國朋友做資訊參考既[不一定有英文]<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fen&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=3d21a7b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/en</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://extradition.g0vhk.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fextradition.g0vhk.io&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=ea505a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://extradition.g0vhk.io</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkchronicles.com&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=b5a31670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkchronicles.com</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有再多既 希望巴打幫手整合全部懷疑被自殺案"},{"pid":"13c3b31ee323c0c1d420d2de868e798d0ad174bb","tid":1573254,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"香港有powpow<br />\n台灣有老高<br />\n<br />\n其他地方仲有冇人知?"},{"pid":"f531dd80ce0d1a8c2e87df7e535c8aacc336529f","tid":1573254,"uid":184581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"標題係<br />\n香港反送中事件引起的離奇命案"},{"pid":"49fe2f89cf6dd8e3d39c6773107006fcd4af37d5","tid":1573254,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人討論下"},{"pid":"3eb58924c0d9a83ff33fdd1b2edda669eb61e6c0","tid":1573254,"uid":303830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"929全球大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1570526/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1570526/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1448ec301ed761c8169bd463813d6d81f23e1804","tid":1573254,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d0d3fff9b8b090c84b1df75299b3cebbc21b2e9","tid":1573254,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:37:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d53d574ddb68878be1788eb528ec56b3c5ce5d6","tid":1573254,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a6e284e54fac2aa7e943f5a313ddc5eaecab5a3","tid":1573254,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20